image_analysis.description: A photograph of a storage closet or utility room filled with various boxes of electrical and lighting supplies. The room has light-colored walls and wooden shelves supported by metal brackets. A vertical black pipe runs through the left side of the shelving. The shelves are cluttered with boxes from brands like Philips, Sunlite, and Elco Lighting. There are also plastic storage drawers and loose items like light bulbs and a lockset box.
image_analysis.layout: Interior shot of a corner storage area with multiple tiers of shelving.
